{"tid":2348842,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"執屋見到CWHK 16 17 ...d 野","createTime":"2021-01-01T05:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T12:17:45.000Z","uid":51753,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1f81e92ee2085d603f2e47f2a2ea594187514fa2","tid":2348842,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:32:19.000Z","msg":"近十年都無去過 呢d 地方唔岩廢老...<br />\n紙袋...當年爭崩頭都想要ge 紙袋而家送俾人都冇人要<br />\n（好在紙袋我一早戒左）<br />\n仲冇好多舊同人誌<br />\n有人想要？ <br />\n送又好 十蚊本又好 <br />\n<br />\n如果呢度有作者想拎番 自己ge 作品<br />\n我可以睇睇有冇<br />\n<br />\n當年個場無咁迫可以做多好多on9 野"},{"pid":"fd5c6d681ae5be9d2c35a15792be84b7ecdb914f","tid":2348842,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:34:41.000Z","msg":"圖?"},{"pid":"097b307454e19783f9bac8fc412f07b4a381fee9","tid":2348842,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fd5c6d681ae5be9d2c35a15792be84b7ecdb914f","tid":2348842,"uid":51148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:34:41.000Z","msg":"圖?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:37:07.000Z","msg":"你想搵番d 書定想要紙袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2483111d8ffd6cb1d8592371074a73abb533fb3c","tid":2348842,"uid":51753,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T05:40:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DUhDYPt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUhDYPt.png&h=3315434b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年要做會員留貨 搶到仆晒街ge REI&rsquo;s ROOM<br />\n紙袋同月曆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇廢老記得"},{"pid":"d2c2b9ec2b5fd82dfc3265968878979b4ef0658c","tid":2348842,"uid":51753,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gQqEuT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gQqEuT.png&h=1e01a2a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有 招收主筆廣告<br />\n當年好興ge 魂。初弒 體筆名而家睇番當然好撚中二<br />\n<br />\n唔知呢檔野執左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de8d06bd33a887eeb6a504323e44b8b069fa854","tid":2348842,"uid":60164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"lm學香港動物史<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95e2322908027f1c9fd38e868df977e3ee3733ee","tid":2348842,"uid":51753,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oyfie9b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOyfie9b.png&h=c90bf683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入場票仲係簡單到冇朋友 <br />\n亦有送一張接駁巴士飛<br />\n當年megabox 未開 果頭真係得狗展<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提 協辦ge 香港美術用品專業中心 上年都執7埋<br />\n無計 要平有馬雲<br />\n要靚可以係Amazon 訂 <br />\n香港租太貴"},{"pid":"0f1681b7a9e4ba74f4652b0d208cd8806e54d408","tid":2348842,"uid":51753,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dD69mTH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdD69mTH.png&h=998ae756&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rwm1Xr7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwm1Xr7.png&h=8d46479b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年最刺激係突然會捉到有架仔檔委托販賣<br />\n無人知佢地會幾時擺d 本出來<br />\n可能2點 可能4點<br />\n捉到完全係你運氣好<br />\n<br />\n因為當年過江龍畫質 係好過local 一大水 <br />\n而且當年要買日本同人誌係相對比較困難<br />\n差不多13 14 算先有機<br />\n<br />\n所以係CW 執到 40 60 蚊咁上下價位買到其實執到寶咁<br />\n當然同人誌就係同人誌 邊度出都逃唔過<br />\n見本 就係唯一會睇果一次 番來都係鋪塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nJH 科學 而家都仲係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be5b7d273a8c2c5f6e13bb2cf2cbf55c811868a","tid":2348842,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jXcktFo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjXcktFo.png&h=52984f94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n襟章都係逃唔過生銹的命運<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n右面3個我好肯定買番來果陣唔係黃色<br />\n但擺左十幾年之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172ebc042631819fe0856f4bf8d4878ec8322f28","tid":2348842,"uid":51753,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T09:10:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hXRQQ2Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhXRQQ2Y.png&h=b126e27d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n十幾年前ge 星夢亭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係黑佢 但而家人地真係進步到對得住大手 呢兩個字<br />\n拿 我更加唔係想黑呀袁才子<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而<br />\n風林<br />\n黑蛛<br />\nHeco@氣球魚屋。。。etc<br />\n果兜就真係一開始已經有一定實力<br />\n我應該有唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e591a57f6b703bf54faee1f79906b581bfa6e2b8","tid":2348842,"uid":51753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T09:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGT7Tq5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGT7Tq5.png&h=1211edd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0D4Gdq9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0D4Gdq9.png&h=b3cb3992&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GEVVhSV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGEVVhSV.png&h=f51ee8b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入場會有d 電影宣傳品派下 例如明信片<br />\n垃圾動畫電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCapura.L 而家仲畫緊<br />\n雖然佢因為專精東方為主做唔成大手<br />\n但十幾年前佢d 畫 同埋本本印刷質素已經係場中top 果批<br />\n不是東方廚的樓主都忍唔住手 買番來封塵<br />\n<br />\n另外當年仲有d 大陸畫師合作的本<br />\n質素可以話係另一個次元<br />\n十幾年前仲係貪曾時代 東莞有ISO <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0c551056f4230251d2e1acf01ae8d0c0afb2e4","tid":2348842,"ui